text: George Kingston may refer to: *George Strickland Kingston (1807–1880), surveyor, architect and politician in South Australia *George Kingston (meteorologist) (1816–1886), Canadian meteorologist *George Kingston (ice hockey) (born 1939), ice hockey coach and the first coach of the San Jose Sharks *George Kingston (carburetor) (1863–1946), inventor of the carburetor *George Frederick Kingston (1889–1950), Canadian Anglican bishop
